<li><a href="/wiki/Rhysling_Award" title="Rhysling Award">Rhysling Award</a> for fantastic poetry</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/James_Tiptree,_Jr._Award" title="James Tiptree, Jr. Award">James Tiptree, Jr. Award</a> for works of science fiction or fantasy that expand or explore our understanding of gender</li>
