<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> Scroll down to the English <a href="http://nagrody.fandom.art.pl/Hugo.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://nagrody.fandom.art.pl/Hugo.html" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.thehugoawards.org/?page_id=11" class="external text" title="http://www.thehugoawards.org/?page_id=11" rel="nofollow">The 1954 Award</a>, thehugoawards.org, retrieved November 3, 2007</li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.locusmag.com/SFAwards/Db/RetroHugo.html" class="external text" title="http://www.locusmag.com/SFAwards/Db/RetroHugo.html" rel="nofollow">The Locus Index to SF Awards: About the Retro-Hugos</a>, retrieved <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-04-24"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="04-24"><a href="/wiki/April_24" title="April 24">April 24</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a></span>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.locusmag.com/2006/Features/AnalysisOfThePoll.html" class="external text" title="http://www.locusmag.com/2006/Features/AnalysisOfThePoll.html" rel="nofollow">Locus Online: Analysis of Locus 2006 Poll &amp; Survey</a></li>
</ol>
