nial (short story) (page does not exist)">Tricentennial</a>” by <a href="/wiki/Joe_Haldeman" title="Joe Haldeman">Joe Haldeman</a> (1977)&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">“<a href="/wiki/Jeffty_Is_Five" title="Jeffty Is Five">Jeffty Is Five</a>” by <a href="/wiki/Harlan_Ellison" title="Harlan Ellison">Harlan Ellison</a> (1978)&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">“<a href="/wiki/Cassandra_(story)" title="Cassandra (story)">Cassandra</a>” by <a href="/wiki/C._J._Cherryh" title="C. J. Cherryh">C. J. Cherryh</a> (1979)&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">“<a href="/wiki/The_Way_of_Cross_and_Dragon" title="The Way of Cross and Dragon">The Way of Cross and Dragon</a>” by <a href="/wiki/George_R._R._Martin" title="George R. R. Martin">George R. R. Martin</a> (1980)</span></p>
